  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Sri Lanka: Strengthening the Capacity to Mitigate Illegal, Unreported and Unregulated Fishing Practices through Introduction of an Integrated Vessel Monitoring System (VMS)</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The project will contribute to strengthening the maritime border management framework of Sri Lanka. The objective is that the Government effectively regulates and operates Multi-day Fishing Vessel fleet reinforcing illegal, unreported and unregulated regulation and to strengthening the government efforts in countering irregular migration, drug trafficking and other cross border criminal activities.</narrative>
  </description>
